// Best-effort cargo-pup config expressing the §11 forbidden edge wcore -> wai.
// P32's open question is exactly whether cargo-pup's schema can state this; the
// CI job runs pup as `continue-on-error` and captures the real outcome, while
// the stable-metadata fallback gate (§3.5) is the hard assertion. If this RON
// shape is wrong, that error IS the evidence that §11 should lean on the
// metadata gate rather than the nightly source lint.
Pup(
    lints: [
        ArchitectureLint(
            name: "core-must-not-depend-on-ai",
            forbidden: [
                (from: "wcore", to: "wai"),
            ],
        ),
    ],
)
